        <abstract> 
<p>Has read MS of AM’s review [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, read at Edinburgh Royal Society, 20 Feb 1860]; has no complaints. Has never heard of a hostile reviewer’s doing so kind and generous an action [as sending his MS for CD’s criticism?]. Sends some remarks on details.</p> 
        </abstract>
